<li><a href="https://controllerstech.com/stm32-freertos-semaphores/">Using Semaphores in CMSIS RTOS</a></li>



<li><a href="https://controllerstech.com/stm32-freertos-mutex/">Using Mutexes in CMSIS RTOS</a></li>



