<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center">STM32 FreeRTOS Stack Monitor Task: Implementation</h2>



<p>A monitor task is a dedicated FreeRTOS task that continuously observes the stack usage of other tasks without interfering with them.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Retrieving Stack Information from Tasks</h3>



<p>We will Use <code>osThreadGetStackSpace()</code> to read the free stack space from each task. The function requires a task handle as parameter:</p>



